text: Saulius Skvernelis (born 23 July 1970) is a Lithuanian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Lithuania from 2016 until 2020. He is also a member of the Seimas. Previously he served as police commissioner, and he was Minister of the Interior from 2014 to 2016. == Other websites == Category:1970 births Category:Prime ministers of Lithuania Category:Police officers Category:People from Kaunas Category:Living people
title: Saulius Skvernelis
